So, come on, let's get to know each other!

373
00:22:23,050 --> 00:22:25,130
If you try anything to me, I'll scream!

374
00:22:25,430 --> 00:22:27,920
Don't be so tense, Yawara-chan!

375
00:22:28,490 --> 00:22:31,150
You gotta take care of your fans, 
right Yawara-chan?

376
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:33,450
Right, Yawara-chan!

377
00:22:33,990 --> 00:22:34,550
Yawara?

378
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:37,390
Yawara? The one that threw Yuki Tohdoh?

379
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,590
That ippon zeoi girl, Yawara Inokuma?

380
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:41,270
That's right!

381
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:45,420
Everyone, she is Yawara Inokuma!

382
00:22:45,930 --> 00:22:46,390
Geez!

383
00:22:55,590 --> 00:22:59,310
That's it! Now I'm mad!

384
00:23:02,330 --> 00:23:03,360
What are you doing?

385
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:06,360
Please don't get so violent!

386
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:08,700
I am not being violent!

387
00:23:08,930 --> 00:23:10,530
Hurry up and change into your dogis!
[dogis : judo uniforms]

