00:23:27,100 --> 00:23:29,220
He will not get away with this!


392
00:23:29,360 --> 00:23:29,850
What's that?

393
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:33,850
Training starts tomorrow! Oh yeah, we should do early morning sessions, too!

